snippet.title: Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 - Season 4: Vondel Reveal Trailer | Summer Game Fest 2023
snippet.description:
Call of Duty Season 4 is coming, introducing an all new Warzone map, a new operator and more. Call of Duty Season 4 drops June 14. You can play the game on PS5, Xbox Series X|S and PC. 

#IGN #SoG #Gaming
